it
engages all the way, or had it 180 degrees out and it slipped off.
There
should be a spring in the hole in the dizzy drive gear that is still in
the
motor.

The gear that the dizzy goes into can be ANYWHERE...........as long as
it is
meshing underneath, and the van will run as it did................Just
put
it back in and time it...........you are not getting it in all the way.


